<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><note xmlns="http://note.youdao.com" file-version="0" schema-version="1.0.3"><head/><body><para><coId>9944-1618303143254</coId><text/><inline-styles/><styles/></para><image><coId>2337-1618303143254</coId><source>https://note.youdao.com/yws/res/13313/D8CF59753F8C4314BBE83098D68E391E</source><text/><styles><width>366</width><height>354</height></styles></image><heading compat="true" level="1"><coId>9450-1618303143254</coId><text>1、SpringMVC自动配置概览</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>17</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles><line-height>1.2857142857142858</line-height></styles></heading><para><coId>7457-1618909865422</coId><text>Spring Boot provides auto-configuration for Spring MVC that works well with most applications.(大多场景我们都无需自定义配置)</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>110</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>8837-1618909865422</coId><text>The auto-configuration adds the following features on top of Spring’s defaults:</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>79</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>7339-1618909865422</coId><text>• Inclusion of ContentNegotiatingViewResolver and BeanNameViewResolver beans.</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>77</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>7867-1618909865422</coId><text>• 内容协商视图解析器和BeanName视图解析器</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>25</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>9867-1618909865422</coId><text>• Support for serving static resources, including support for WebJars (covered later in this document)).</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>104</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>6000-1618909865422</coId><text>• 静态资源（包括webjars）</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>17</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>6732-1618909865422</coId><text>• Automatic registration of Converter, GenericConverter, and Formatter beans.</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>77</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>3697-1618909865422</coId><text>• 自动注册 Converter，GenericConverter，Formatter </text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>44</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>5588-1618909865422</coId><text>• Support for HttpMessageConverters (covered later in this document).</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>69</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>8876-1618909865422</coId><text>• 支持 HttpMessageConverters （后来我们配合内容协商理解原理）</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>43</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>1128-1618909865422</coId><text>• Automatic registration of MessageCodesResolver (covered later in this document).</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>82</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>8397-1618909865422</coId><text>• 自动注册 MessageCodesResolver （国际化用）</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>34</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>9887-1618909865422</coId><text>• Static index.html support.</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>28</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>7159-1618909865422</coId><text>• 静态index.html 页支持</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>18</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>9290-1618909865422</coId><text>• Custom Favicon support (covered later in this document).</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>58</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>4215-1618909865422</coId><text>• 自定义 Favicon  </text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>15</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>2518-1618909865422</coId><text>• Automatic use of a ConfigurableWebBindingInitializer bean (covered later in this document).</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>93</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>9340-1618909865422</coId><text>• 自动使用 ConfigurableWebBindingInitializer ，（DataBinder负责将请求数据绑定到JavaBean上）</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>73</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>7213-1618909867523</coId><text/><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>2450-1618909868273</coId><text/><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>1870-1618909868386</coId><text>If you want to keep those Spring Boot MVC customizations and make more MVC customizations (interceptors, formatters, view controllers, and other features), you can add your own @Configuration class of type WebMvcConfigurer but without @EnableWebMvc.</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>249</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>7688-1618909878136</coId><text>不用@EnableWebMvc注解。使用 @Configuration + WebMvcConfigurer 自定义规则</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>60</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>2587-1618909878136</coId><text>If you want to provide custom instances of RequestMappingHandlerMapping, RequestMappingHandlerAdapter, or ExceptionHandlerExceptionResolver, and still keep the Spring Boot MVC customizations, you can declare a bean of type WebMvcRegistrations and use it to provide custom instances of those components.</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>302</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>0026-1618909878136</coId><text>声明 WebMvcRegistrations 改变默认底层组件</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>31</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>1144-1618909878136</coId><text>If you want to take complete control of Spring MVC, you can add your own @Configuration annotated with @EnableWebMvc, or alternatively add your own @Configuration-annotated DelegatingWebMvcConfiguration as described in the Javadoc of @EnableWebMvc.</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>248</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para><para><coId>9087-1618909878136</coId><text>使用 @EnableWebMvc+@Configuration+DelegatingWebMvcConfiguration 全面接管SpringMVC</text><inline-styles><font-size><from>0</from><to>75</to><value>16</value></font-size></inline-styles><styles/></para></body></note>